original_title: Dinosaur Train: Classic in the Jurassic
overview: Join Buddy and his friends on the Dinosaur Train, as they participate in the greatest dinosaur sporting event of all time, The Classic in the Jurassic. Different Species from the Triassic, Jurassic and Cretaceous time periods compete against each other to see who is the best at racing, swimming and flying.  Includes 6 stories plus Dr Scott teaches us more about the real-life world of dinosaurs.
title: Dinosaur Train: Classic in the Jurassic
